---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<MainLayout title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION}>
	<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-20">
		<!-- Hero -->
		<section class="mb-24">
			<h1 class="font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
				<span class="text-8xl max-md:text-6xl block">We Build</span>
				<span class="text-4xl max-md:text-2xl text-gray-300 block">&gt; AI Agents</span>
				<span class="text-4xl max-md:text-2xl text-gray-300 block">&gt; Automated Workflows</span>
				<span class="text-4xl max-md:text-2xl text-gray-300 block">&gt; Solutions to Your Problems</span>
			</h1>
			<p class="text-xl mb-8 max-w-2xl">
				<span class="text-white font-bold">New Age. New Problems. New Solutions.</span><br />
				<span class="text-gray-400">We fix ops, reduce costs, and grow your business. We use AI and develop automations to help your business grow. We want to help. A passion for helping is our middle name. Tell us about your business, and help us, help you improve your business.</span>
			</p>
			<a href="https://cal.com/thejeffdo/30min" class="inline-block py-3 px-6 bg-white text-black no-underline rounded-lg font-medium transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-gray-200" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Let's Build</a>
		</section>

		<!-- 01/ Offers -->
		<section class="mb-24">
			<div class="flex items-baseline gap-4 mb-8">
				<span class="text-gray-500 text-sm font-medium">01/</span>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Offers</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-md:grid-cols-1">
				<div class="p-8 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl">
					<div class="flex items-baseline gap-3 mb-4">
						<span class="text-gray-500 text-lg">01</span>
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Development Services</h3>
					</div>
					<p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">We audit your business, find what's costing you time and money, and build AI solutions to your problems in weeks. We analyze data, create pipelines, handle end to end development, and improve your systems.</p>
					<a href="https://cal.com/thejeffdo/30min" class="inline-block py-3 px-6 bg-white text-black no-underline rounded-lg font-medium transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-gray-200" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Let's Build</a>
				</div>
				<div class="p-8 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl">
					<div class="flex items-baseline gap-3 mb-4">
						<span class="text-gray-500 text-lg">02</span>
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Partnerships</h3>
					</div>
					<p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">You know your industry, you just don't know how to build it. We are the solution. Performance based model, where if you win, we win. We grow when you grow. You bring the expertise, and we bring in the dev team.</p>
					<a href="https://cal.com/thejeffdo/30min" class="inline-block py-3 px-6 bg-white text-black no-underline rounded-lg font-medium transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-gray-200" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Let's Partner</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- 02/ Why Automate -->
		<section class="mb-24">
			<div class="flex items-baseline gap-4 mb-8">
				<span class="text-gray-500 text-sm font-medium">02/</span>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Why Automate</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="space-y-8 max-w-3xl">
				<p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Times are changing. Your competitors are already automating their workflows, cutting costs, and moving faster than ever. The question isn't whether to automate—it's how quickly you can start.</p>
				<p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">If you aren't growing, you're dying. AI automation unlocks scale without proportional cost increases. What used to require a team of 10 can now be handled by systems that work 24/7 with consistent precision.</p>
				<p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Speed. Accuracy. Savings. And making more money. Cut operational costs while increasing output. Free your team to focus on what actually matters—growing the business.</p>
				<p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">What would have taken months, can now happen in weeks. You just need the team that knows how.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- 03/ Why Partner -->
		<section class="mb-24">
			<div class="flex items-baseline gap-4 mb-8">
				<span class="text-gray-500 text-sm font-medium">03/</span>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Why Partner</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="space-y-8 max-w-3xl">
				<p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Think of us as AI experts in your pocket. We bring new possibilities to your business—experienced engineers who have built systems across 50+ projects, now focused entirely on helping your business thrive.</p>
				<p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">We're builders. We build, and solve problems. Not create slide decks.</p>
				<p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Relentless helpfulness is our default mode. We're not satisfied until you're succeeding. When we partner on outcomes, your growth is our growth. We win when you win.</p>
				<p class="text-xl text-white font-medium">We are the kind of team you want in your corner. It's a win-win.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- 04/ FAQ -->
		<section class="mb-24">
			<div class="flex items-baseline gap-4 mb-12">
				<span class="text-gray-500 text-sm font-medium">04/</span>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">FAQ</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="space-y-4">
				<details class="group border-b border-gray-700 pb-4">
					<summary class="flex items-baseline gap-4 cursor-pointer list-none">
						<span class="text-gray-500 text-sm">01/</span>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white flex-1">How are we different?</h3>
						<span class="text-gray-500 group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform text-xl">+</span>
					</summary>
					<p class="text-gray-400 pl-10 pt-4">We sell outcomes to help you the most. If you need a 1 person, 8 person, or 0 person dev team, we figure it out together. We build quick and fast, whatever is the best fit for you, and the AI future.</p>
				</details>
				<details class="group border-b border-gray-700 pb-4">
					<summary class="flex items-baseline gap-4 cursor-pointer list-none">
						<span class="text-gray-500 text-sm">02/</span>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white flex-1">What if we don't know what we need yet?</h3>
						<span class="text-gray-500 group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform text-xl">+</span>
					</summary>
					<p class="text-gray-400 pl-10 pt-4">That's what the call is for. You tell us your business, what you need done the most, and we help build that first. Zero prep needed, give us your problems, we will give you solutions.</p>
				</details>
				<details class="group border-b border-gray-700 pb-4">
					<summary class="flex items-baseline gap-4 cursor-pointer list-none">
						<span class="text-gray-500 text-sm">03/</span>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white flex-1">How does pricing work?</h3>
						<span class="text-gray-500 group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform text-xl">+</span>
					</summary>
					<p class="text-gray-400 pl-10 pt-4">Whatever is best for you. Flat fees, partnerships, retainers, fractional ownership. Different scope, different industries, different margins, give us a call, and we will let you know what can work for us.</p>
				</details>
				<details class="group border-b border-gray-700 pb-4">
					<summary class="flex items-baseline gap-4 cursor-pointer list-none">
						<span class="text-gray-500 text-sm">04/</span>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white flex-1">How fast are you?</h3>
						<span class="text-gray-500 group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform text-xl">+</span>
					</summary>
					<p class="text-gray-400 pl-10 pt-4">We deliver in weeks, not months. You can see the first value within a week. We will send updates, as work is performed. Full system builds take longer, but can be completed within 1-2 months.</p>
				</details>
				<details class="group border-b border-gray-700 pb-4">
					<summary class="flex items-baseline gap-4 cursor-pointer list-none">
						<span class="text-gray-500 text-sm">05/</span>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white flex-1">What kind of businesses do you work with?</h3>
						<span class="text-gray-500 group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform text-xl">+</span>
					</summary>
					<p class="text-gray-400 pl-10 pt-4">We work with companies looking to figure out how to build faster processes, using AI and tech. We are industry agnostic, handling tech for ecommerce, real estate, manufacturing, travel, service businesses, and more. If you have a workflow you want to automate, call us.</p>
				</details>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- CTA -->
		<section class="text-center py-16 border-t border-gray-700">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Ready or Not?</h2>
			<p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">Let's discuss how we can help your business thrive.</p>
			<a href="https://cal.com/thejeffdo/30min" class="inline-block py-3 px-6 bg-white text-black no-underline rounded-lg font-medium transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-gray-200" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Let's Build</a>
		</section>

	</div>
</MainLayout>
